OL,3,CResidents told to stay indoors after
OL,4,Cfire at Scottish recycling centre
OL,6,FResidents living nearby to a fire
OL,7,Fwhich broke out at an electrical and
OL,8,Fbattery recycling treatment facility
OL,9,Fin the Scottish town of Paisley
OL,10,Fovernight have been urged to remain
OL,11,Findoors and to keep their windows and
OL,12,Fdoors shut.
OL,14,FUp to 10 crews were mobilised to
OL,15,Ftackle the blaze at the Linwood
OL,16,FIndustrial Estate just after 9pm on
OL,17,FSunday, following reports of a fire in
OL,18,Fa commercial building on Burnbrae
OL,19,FRoad, the Scottish Fire and Rescue
OL,20,FService said.
