OL,4,Cfire at Scottish recycling centre
OL,6,FHe added: "While smoke continues to be
OL,7,Fvisible, we would ask that residents
OL,8,Fremain indoors and keep windows and
OL,9,Fdoors closed as a precaution.
OL,11,F"If travelling through smoke,
OL,12,Fmotorists should keep windows closed,
OL,13,Fturn off air conditioning and keep
OL,14,Ftheir air vents closed."
